{"tid":399470,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[性本善] 第一次反包皮","createTime":"2017-09-14T03:39:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T11:20:05.000Z","uid":143011,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fb016d919ec811da5b7819f494c452eb4638b5ad","tid":399470,"uid":143011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:39:09.000Z","msg":"老豆老母一路都冇講過要反<br />\n十幾年黎都冇反過<br />\n前兩日的起心肝試下反，晚晚都練反半個鐘<br />\n依家冇扯可以輕鬆反到龜頭後面<br />\n但係扯左就淨係反到龜頭一半反唔哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  可以點搞<br />\n同埋係咪要反到落底定係過龜頭就可以？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n請賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d526a47944af327569ed8f328936cebc21d0aec","tid":399470,"uid":51080,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:41:02.000Z","msg":"再反落去會成個龜頭甩出黎，千祈唔好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申: 試過，自己放唔返落去，要入醫院搞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa8392ab23f5ed03a8d4ae769c909ae1ca64e7c1","tid":399470,"uid":11067,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T04:39:08.000Z","msg":"日日都洗 洗乾淨啲白色珍珠<br />\n咁就易反好多"},{"pid":"dafd69d142b62a7679e96622b778605def2b1c2c","tid":399470,"uid":51080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T00:31:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日日都洗 洗乾淨啲白色珍珠<br />\n咁就易反好多</blockquote><br />\n洗得走嘅咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我有粒喺度好多年，日日洗好乾淨都重喺度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45d0037ae5282d2ecdf8408883688e9646425fa4","tid":399470,"uid":59780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T00:32:48.000Z","msg":"浸浴反易好多"},{"pid":"9bf1da192f273e3dd9f6f96b613b4bc88a2a0c1e","tid":399470,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09